    "body": "I agree that this is currently a very simple model. It plays the flame overlay and the more incendiary damage is done, the larger the flame gets. Having flame based weapons deal damage over time with appropriate animations is a pull request of it's own. See https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/7115.\n"
